data.title: Natsuna Watanabe
data.meta_description:
Natsuna Watanabe was born on May 23, 1989, in Saitama Prefecture, Japan. She grew up in a family that was not involved in the entertainment industry. However, she developed an interest in acting at a young age and decided to pursue it as a career.
